title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 213: Featuring Duncan Keith
description:
On Monday's episode of Spittin' Chiclets, the guys are joined by 3x Stanley Cup Champion, Duncan Keith. Duncan joins to talk about the Blackhawks dynasty, winning gold medals, some funny stories about teammates and more. The boys also recap their trip to Chicago, including the Blackhawks “Shoot The Puck” intermission video. Ryan missed his shot. But was he sabotaged? He discussed on Monday's episode. Rear Ads wraps up with a gambling corner and the guys touch on some NHL news.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
